    www.BioNeuroTech.com

    Multidisciplinary Neuroscientific Technologies Ltd

    --- MISSION STATEMENT ---

    (1) Exploring and experimenting with computing engineering software technologies.

    (2) Exploring how these can be merged with biosciences/neurosciences at all levels of structural organisation.

    (3) Developing computational models of neurobiological systems; and implementing neural approaches to computing.

    (4) Applying these resources to practical ways of solving real-world everyday-life complex problems.

          IML: Interactive Deep Machine Learning Data Apps (webpage-based)

           

           

          This webpage in in the process of being set-up, please check again in several months.

          ​

          ​

          What will be done:

          ​

          My PythonAnywhere scripts, will be linked to Plesk, PHP/SQL scripts and the Flask micro-framework system.

          ​

          Google Cloud Platform TPUs (tensor processing units) will be used to train and test neuroimaging data.

          ​

          This will be implemented as an interactive app directly in this site's webpage, which users can use to input data and extract data.

          ​

          ​

          ​

          ​

          ​

          ​

          ​

          See sections C-NhaNp-S and C-Cogn-S for now.
